      "comment": "BROOMBRAE TOMMY (2) turned in a plain run last time when sixth at this track over 390m behind Moe Patty (23.05) in a Grade 5. Has ability and looks hard to stop. JOHN BOY (7) jumped from the inside and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten a long neck (22.96) behind Bella Supreme at Warrnambool. Will give a great sight again. LIKE A BLAZE (6) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (25.01) at Bendigo in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Can hit the frame this time. BLACK CABANG (1) can sneak into the finish.",
